data.description: A unique home nestled in the heart of Fostoria, Ohio. This inviting residence offers a blend of comfort, convenience, and timeless appeal.   The main level features a spacious living area, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply relaxing with loved ones. The adjoining kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and plenty of counter space for meal preparation.  This home can offer 8 bedrooms, including a large master suite that needs finishing touches.   The property could also be income producing and split into 4-6 separate units. 3 staircases & entrances.
